{"tid":1285900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下各大院校咪撚對話/閉門會議","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T18:17:14.000Z","uid":36158,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"72bdd56932fc3b21655991f4681b773f083b15c6","tid":1285900,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"對話其實即係談判<br />\n談判即係其中一方或者雙方讓步<br />\n我地應該企硬 如果唔係對唔住義士<br />\n再加上每項訴求入邊到底有邊樣可以讓?<br />\n我地唔讓 咁要對話黎做乜?<br />\n<br />\n有人會話/支持論點<br />\n對話可以令佢直接回應 唔岩聽可以屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n第一，雨革既經驗已經話過比我地知 <br />\n對話係無撚用 <br />\n當年係串得好開心啊<br />\n但係到頭黎乜都爭取左d乜野?<br />\n<br />\n第二，我地既行動目的並唔係為左落林奠面<br />\n唔該記返起走左義士既遺願<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係個五大訴求啊！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n呢五大訴求係完全無讓步既餘地架！！<br />\n讓撚左佢地唔會安息架！！<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n無野好傾"},{"pid":"e754245adf30bed238bff1726010b5f4040cc727","tid":1285900,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d3e79ad46997cc05b8466f5d426a21f4c2ecc31","tid":1285900,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"97123e202443229a620dfe7365a13b433788a1c4","tid":1285900,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我無野講"},{"pid":"bf8a692712b4a23cdbcb0d8f22f293f15a8bc7c0","tid":1285900,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba288737b9db23c799f81a43dc5470824fa9ac45","tid":1285900,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"802ab87940145833eedf5dfda23ca83d8ee1cd2d","tid":1285900,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你冇野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ed9a4d937ad12b6b22db57925b44356e4e193398","tid":1285900,"uid":3